				</td>
						<td class="crayon-code"><div class="crayon-pre" style="font-size: 12px !important; line-height: 15px !important; -moz-tab-size:4; -o-tab-size:4; -webkit-tab-size:4; tab-size:4;"><div class="crayon-line" id="crayon-623de9e82a446229986476-1">&nbsp;</div><div class="crayon-line" id="crayon-623de9e82a446229986476-2"><span class="crayon-h">&lt;</span><span class="crayon-sy">?</span><span class="crayon-e">php</span></div><div class="crayon-line" id="crayon-623de9e82a446229986476-3">&nbsp;</div><div class="crayon-line" id="crayon-623de9e82a446229986476-4"><span class="crayon-st">if</span><span class="crayon-h"> </span><span class="crayon-sy">(</span></div><div class="crayon-line" id="crayon-623de9e82a446229986476-5"><span class="crayon-h">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span class="crayon-sy">$</span><span class="crayon-i">expr1</span></div><div class="crayon-line" id="crayon-623de9e82a446229986476-6"><span class="crayon-h">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>&amp;&amp;<span class="crayon-h"> </span><span class="crayon-sy">$</span><span class="crayon-i">expr2</span></div><div class="crayon-line" id="crayon-623de9e82a446229986476-7"><span class="crayon-sy">)</span><span class="crayon-h"> </span><span class="crayon-sy">{</span></div><div class="crayon-line" id="crayon-623de9e82a446229986476-8"><span class="crayon-h">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span class="crayon-c">// if body</span></div><div class="crayon-line" id="crayon-623de9e82a446229986476-9"><span class="crayon-sy">}</span><span class="crayon-h"> </span><span class="crayon-st">elseif</span><span class="crayon-h"> </span><span class="crayon-sy">(</span></div><div class="crayon-line" id="crayon-623de9e82a446229986476-10"><span class="crayon-h">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span class="crayon-sy">$</span><span class="crayon-i">expr3</span></div><div class="crayon-line" id="crayon-623de9e82a446229986476-11"><span class="crayon-h">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>&amp;&amp;<span class="crayon-h"> </span><span class="crayon-sy">$</span><span class="crayon-i">expr4</span></div><div class="crayon-line" id="crayon-623de9e82a446229986476-12"><span class="crayon-sy">)</span><span class="crayon-h"> </span><span class="crayon-sy">{</span></div><div class="crayon-line" id="crayon-623de9e82a446229986476-13"><span class="crayon-h">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span class="crayon-c">// elseif body</span></div><div class="crayon-line" id="crayon-623de9e82a446229986476-14"><span class="crayon-sy">}</span><span class="crayon-h">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></div><div class="crayon-line" id="crayon-623de9e82a446229986476-15">&nbsp;</div></div></td>
					</tr>
				</tbody></table>
			</div>
		</div>
<!-- [Format Time: 0.0007 seconds] -->
<p></p>
<h6>5.2 switch, case</h6>
<p>Структура <code>switch</code> выглядит следующим образом. Обратите 
внимание на расположение скобок, пробелов и фигурных скобок. Оператор 
case ДОЛЖЕН отделяться от <code>switch</code> одним отступом, а ключевое слово <code>break</code>
 (или другие завершающие ключевые слова) ДОЛЖНО иметь отступ на том же 
уровне, что и тело case. ДОЛЖЕН быть комментарий, такой как <code>// no break</code>, когда fall-through является преднамеренным в непустом теле <code>case</code>.</p>
<p></p><!-- Crayon Syntax Highlighter v_2.7.2_beta -->
<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="PSR-12_files/classic-copy.css">
<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="PSR-12_files/monaco.css">

		<div id="crayon-623de9e82a447252746724" class="crayon-syntax crayon-theme-classic-copy crayon-font-monaco crayon-os-pc print-yes notranslate" data-settings=" minimize scroll-mouseover" style="max-width: 900px; margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; font-size: 12px !important; line-height: 15px !important; height: auto;">
		
			<div class="crayon-plain-wrap"><textarea class="crayon-plain print-no" data-settings="dblclick" readonly="readonly" style="tab-size: 4; font-size: 12px !important; line-height: 15px !important; z-index: 0; opacity: 0; overflow: hidden;" wrap="soft">
&lt;?php

switch ($expr) {
    case 0:
        echo 'First case, with a break';
        break;
    case 1:
        echo 'Second case, which falls through';
        // no break
    case 2:
    case 3:
    case 4:
        echo 'Third case, return instead of break';
        return;
    default:
        echo 'Default case';
        break;
}	
</textarea></div>
			<div class="crayon-main" style="max-width: 900px; position: relative; z-index: 1; overflow: hidden;">
				<table class="crayon-table" style="margin-left: -25px;">
					<tbody><tr class="crayon-row">
				<td class="crayon-nums " data-settings="hide">
					<div class="crayon-nums-content" style="font-size: 12px !important; line-height: 15px !important;"><div class="crayon-num" data-line="crayon-623de9e82a447252746724-1">1</div><div class="crayon-num" data-line="crayon-623de9e82a447252746724-2">2</div><div class="crayon-num" data-line="crayon-623de9e82a447252746724-3">3</div><div class="crayon-num" data-line="crayon-623de9e82a447252746724-4">4</div><div class="crayon-num" data-line="crayon-623de9e82a447252746724-5">5</div><div class="crayon-num" data-line="crayon-623de9e82a447252746724-6">6</div><div class="crayon-num" data-line="crayon-623de9e82a447252746724-7">7</div><div class="crayon-num" data-line="crayon-623de9e82a447252746724-8">8</div><div class="crayon-num" data-line="crayon-623de9e82a447252746724-9">9</div><div class="crayon-num" data-line="crayon-623de9e82a447252746724-10">10</div><div class="crayon-num" data-line="crayon-623de9e82a447252746724-11">11</div><div class="crayon-num" data-line="crayon-623de9e82a447252746724-12">12</div><div class="crayon-num" data-line="crayon-623de9e82a447252746724-13">13</div><div class="crayon-num" data-line="crayon-623de9e82a447252746724-14">14</div><div class="crayon-num" data-line="crayon-623de9e82a447252746724-15">15</div><div class="crayon-num" data-line="crayon-623de9e82a447252746724-16">16</div><div class="crayon-num" data-line="crayon-623de9e82a447252746724-17">17</div><div class="crayon-num" data-line="crayon-623de9e82a447252746724-18">18</div><div class="crayon-num" data-line="crayon-623de9e82a447252746724-19">19</div><div class="crayon-num" data-line="crayon-623de9e82a447252746724-20">20</div></div>
				</td>
						<td class="crayon-code"><div class="crayon-pre" style="font-size: 12px !important; line-height: 15px !important; -moz-tab-size:4; -o-tab-size:4; -webkit-tab-size:4; tab-size:4;"><div class="crayon-line" id="crayon-623de9e82a447252746724-1">&nbsp;</div><div class="crayon-line" id="crayon-623de9e82a447252746724-2"><span class="crayon-h">&lt;</span><span class="crayon-sy">?</span><span class="crayon-e">php</span></div><div class="crayon-line" id="crayon-623de9e82a447252746724-3">&nbsp;</div><div class="crayon-line" id="crayon-623de9e82a447252746724-4"><span class="crayon-st">switch</span><span class="crayon-h"> </span><span class="crayon-sy">(</span><span class="crayon-sy">$</span><span class="crayon-i">expr</span><span class="crayon-sy">)</span><span class="crayon-h"> </span><span class="crayon-sy">{</span></div><div class="crayon-line" id="crayon-623de9e82a447252746724-5"><span class="crayon-h">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span class="crayon-st">case</span><span class="crayon-h"> </span><span class="crayon-cn">0</span><span class="crayon-sy">:</span></div><div class="crayon-line" id="crayon-623de9e82a447252746724-6"><span class="crayon-h">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span class="crayon-i">echo</span><span class="crayon-h"> </span><span class="crayon-s">'First case, with a break'</span><span class="crayon-sy">;</span></div><div class="crayon-line" id="crayon-623de9e82a447252746724-7"><span class="crayon-h">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span class="crayon-st">break</span><span class="crayon-sy">;</span></div><div class="crayon-line" id="crayon-623de9e82a447252746724-8"><span class="crayon-h">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span class="crayon-st">case</span><span class="crayon-h"> </span><span class="crayon-cn">1</span><span class="crayon-sy">:</span></div><div class="crayon-line" id="crayon-623de9e82a447252746724-9"><span class="crayon-h">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span class="crayon-i">echo</span><span class="crayon-h"> </span><span class="crayon-s">'Second case, which falls through'</span><span class="crayon-sy">;</span></div><div class="crayon-line" id="crayon-623de9e82a447252746724-10"><span class="crayon-h">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span class="crayon-c">// no break</span></div><div class="crayon-line" id="crayon-623de9e82a447252746724-11"><span class="crayon-h">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span class="crayon-st">case</span><span class="crayon-h"> </span><span class="crayon-cn">2</span><span class="crayon-sy">:</span></div><div class="crayon-line" id="crayon-623de9e82a447252746724-12"><span class="crayon-h">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span class="crayon-st">case</span><span class="crayon-h"> </span><span class="crayon-cn">3</span><span class="crayon-sy">:</span></div><div class="crayon-line" id="crayon-623de9e82a447252746724-13"><span class="crayon-h">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span class="crayon-st">case</span><span class="crayon-h"> </span><span class="crayon-cn">4</span><span class="crayon-sy">:</span></div><div class="crayon-line" id="crayon-623de9e82a447252746724-14"><span class="crayon-h">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span class="crayon-i">echo</span><span class="crayon-h"> </span><span class="crayon-s">'Third case, return instead of break'</span><span class="crayon-sy">;</span></div><div class="crayon-line" id="crayon-623de9e82a447252746724-15"><span class="crayon-h">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span class="crayon-st">return</span><span class="crayon-sy">;</span></div><div class="crayon-line" id="crayon-623de9e82a447252746724-16"><span class="crayon-h">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span class="crayon-st">default</span><span class="crayon-sy">:</span></div><div class="crayon-line" id="crayon-623de9e82a447252746724-17"><span class="crayon-h">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span class="crayon-i">echo</span><span class="crayon-h"> </span><span class="crayon-s">'Default case'</span><span class="crayon-sy">;</span></div><div class="crayon-line" id="crayon-623de9e82a447252746724-18"><span class="crayon-h">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span class="crayon-st">break</span><span class="crayon-sy">;</span></div><div class="crayon-line" id="crayon-623de9e82a447252746724-19"><span class="crayon-sy">}</span><span class="crayon-h">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></div><div class="crayon-line" id="crayon-623de9e82a447252746724-20">&nbsp;</div></div></td>
					</tr>
				</tbody></table>
			</div>
		</div>
<!-- [Format Time: 0.0010 seconds] -->
<p></p>
<p>Выражения в скобках МОГУТ разбиваться на несколько строк, где между 
каждой последующей строкой имеется минимум один отступ. При этом первое 
условие ДОЛЖНО быть на следующей строке. Закрывающая скобка и 
открывающая фигурная скобка ДОЛЖНЫ быть размещены вместе на отдельной 
строке с одним пробелом между ними. Логические операторы между условиями
 всегда ДОЛЖНЫ быть в начале или в конце строки, а не в обоих местах.</p>
<p></p><!-- Crayon Syntax Highlighter v_2.7.2_beta -->
<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="PSR-12_files/classic-copy.css">
<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="PSR-12_files/monaco.css">

		<div id="crayon-623de9e82a449674797340" class="crayon-syntax crayon-theme-classic-copy crayon-font-monaco crayon-os-pc print-yes notranslate" data-settings=" minimize scroll-mouseover" style="max-width: 900px; margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; font-size: 12px !important; line-height: 15px !important; height: auto;">
		
			<div class="crayon-plain-wrap"><textarea class="crayon-plain print-no" data-settings="dblclick" readonly="readonly" style="tab-size: 4; font-size: 12px !important; line-height: 15px !important; z-index: 0; opacity: 0; overflow: hidden;" wrap="soft">
&lt;?php

switch (
    $expr1
    &amp;&amp; $expr2
) {
    // structure body
}	
</textarea></div>
			<div class="crayon-main" style="max-width: 900px; position: relative; z-index: 1; overflow: hidden;">
				<table class="crayon-table" style="margin-left: -25px;">
					<tbody><tr class="crayon-row">
				<td class="crayon-nums " data-settings="hide">
					<div class="crayon-nums-content" style="font-size: 12px !important; line-height: 15px !important;"><div class="crayon-num" data-line="crayon-623de9e82a449674797340-1">1</div><div class="crayon-num" data-line="crayon-623de9e82a449674797340-2">2</div><div class="crayon-num" data-line="crayon-623de9e82a449674797340-3">3</div><div class="crayon-num" data-line="crayon-623de9e82a449674797340-4">4</div><div class="crayon-num" data-line="crayon-623de9e82a449674797340-5">5</div><div class="crayon-num" data-line="crayon-623de9e82a449674797340-6">6</div><div class="crayon-num" data-line="crayon-623de9e82a449674797340-7">7</div><div class="crayon-num" data-line="crayon-623de9e82a449674797340-8">8</div><div class="crayon-num" data-line="crayon-623de9e82a449674797340-9">9</div><div class="crayon-num" data-line="crayon-623de9e82a449674797340-10">10</div></div>
				</td>
						<td class="crayon-code"><div class="crayon-pre" style="font-size: 12px !important; line-height: 15px !important; -moz-tab-size:4; -o-tab-size:4; -webkit-tab-size:4; tab-size:4;"><div class="crayon-line" id="crayon-623de9e82a449674797340-1">&nbsp;</div><div class="crayon-line" id="crayon-623de9e82a449674797340-2"><span class="crayon-h">&lt;</span><span class="crayon-sy">?</span><span class="crayon-e">php</span></div><div class="crayon-line" id="crayon-623de9e82a449674797340-3">&nbsp;</div><div class="crayon-line" id="crayon-623de9e82a449674797340-4"><span class="crayon-st">switch</span><span class="crayon-h"> </span><span class="crayon-sy">(</span></div><div class="crayon-line" id="crayon-623de9e82a449674797340-5"><span class="crayon-h">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span class="crayon-sy">$</span><span class="crayon-i">expr1</span></div><div class="crayon-line" id="crayon-623de9e82a449674797340-6"><span class="crayon-h">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>&amp;&amp;<span class="crayon-h"> </span><span class="crayon-sy">$</span><span class="crayon-i">expr2</span></div><div class="crayon-line" id="crayon-623de9e82a449674797340-7"><span class="crayon-sy">)</span><span class="crayon-h"> </span><span class="crayon-sy">{</span></div><div class="crayon-line" id="crayon-623de9e82a449674797340-8"><span class="crayon-h">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span class="crayon-c">// structure body</span></div><div class="crayon-line" id="crayon-623de9e82a449674797340-9"><span class="crayon-sy">}</span><span class="crayon-h">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></div><div class="crayon-line" id="crayon-623de9e82a449674797340-10">&nbsp;</div></div></td>
					</tr>
				</tbody></table>
			</div>
		</div>
<!-- [Format Time: 0.0002 seconds] -->
<p></p>
<h6>5.3 while, do while</h6>
<p>Оператор <code>while</code> выглядит следующим образом. Обратите внимание на расположение скобок, пробелов, и фигурных скобок.</p>
<p></p><!-- Crayon Syntax Highlighter v_2.7.2_beta -->
<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="PSR-12_files/classic-copy.css">
<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="PSR-12_files/monaco.css">

		<div id="crayon-623de9e82a44d222951110" class="crayon-syntax crayon-theme-classic-copy crayon-font-monaco crayon-os-pc print-yes notranslate" data-settings=" minimize scroll-mouseover" style="max-width: 900px; margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; font-size: 12px !important; line-height: 15px !important; height: auto;">
		
			<div class="crayon-plain-wrap"><textarea class="crayon-plain print-no" data-settings="dblclick" readonly="readonly" style="tab-size: 4; font-size: 12px !important; line-height: 15px !important; z-index: 0; opacity: 0; overflow: hidden;" wrap="soft">
&lt;?php

while ($expr) {
    // structure body
}	
</textarea></div>
			<div class="crayon-main" style="max-width: 900px; position: relative; z-index: 1; overflow: hidden;">
				<table class="crayon-table" style="margin-left: -18px;">
					<tbody><tr class="crayon-row">
				<td class="crayon-nums " data-settings="hide">
					<div class="crayon-nums-content" style="font-size: 12px !important; line-height: 15px !important;"><div class="crayon-num" data-line="crayon-623de9e82a44d222951110-1">1</div><div class="crayon-num" data-line="crayon-623de9e82a44d222951110-2">2</div><div class="crayon-num" data-line="crayon-623de9e82a44d222951110-3">3</div><div class="crayon-num" data-line="crayon-623de9e82a44d222951110-4">4</div><div class="crayon-num" data-line="crayon-623de9e82a44d222951110-5">5</div><div class="crayon-num" data-line="crayon-623de9e82a44d222951110-6">6</div><div class="crayon-num" data-line="crayon-623de9e82a44d222951110-7">7</div></div>
				</td>
						<td class="crayon-code"><div class="crayon-pre" style="font-size: 12px !important; line-height: 15px !important; -moz-tab-size:4; -o-tab-size:4; -webkit-tab-size:4; tab-size:4;"><div class="crayon-line" id="crayon-623de9e82a44d222951110-1">&nbsp;</div><div class="crayon-line" id="crayon-623de9e82a44d222951110-2"><span class="crayon-h">&lt;</span><span class="crayon-sy">?</span><span class="crayon-e">php</span></div><div class="crayon-line" id="crayon-623de9e82a44d222951110-3">&nbsp;</div><div class="crayon-line" id="crayon-623de9e82a44d222951110-4"><span class="crayon-st">while</span><span class="crayon-h"> </span><span class="crayon-sy">(</span><span class="crayon-sy">$</span><span class="crayon-i">expr</span><span class="crayon-sy">)</span><span class="crayon-h"> </span><span class="crayon-sy">{</span></div><div class="crayon-line" id="crayon-623de9e82a44d222951110-5"><span class="crayon-h">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span class="crayon-c">// structure body</span></div><div class="crayon-line" id="crayon-623de9e82a44d222951110-6"><span class="crayon-sy">}</span><span class="crayon-h">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></div><div class="crayon-line" id="crayon-623de9e82a44d222951110-7">&nbsp;</div></div></td>
					</tr>
				</tbody></table>
			</div>
		</div>
<!-- [Format Time: 0.0013 seconds] -->
<p></p>
<p>Выражения в скобках МОГУТ разбиваться на несколько строк, где между 
каждой последующей строкой имеется минимум один отступ. При этом первое 
условие ДОЛЖНО быть на следующей строке. Закрывающая скобка и 
открывающая фигурная скобка ДОЛЖНЫ быть размещены вместе на отдельной 
строке с одним пробелом между ними. Логические операторы между условиями
 всегда ДОЛЖНЫ быть в начале или в конце строки, а не в обоих местах.</p>
