<p></p>
<h3>8. Анонимные классы</h3>
<p>Анонимные классы ДОЛЖНЫ следовать тем же рекомендациям и принципам, что и закрытие в вышеприведенном разделе.</p>
<p></p><!-- Crayon Syntax Highlighter v_2.7.2_beta -->
<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="PSR-12_files/classic-copy.css">
<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="PSR-12_files/monaco.css">

		<div id="crayon-623de9e82a46b539003283" class="crayon-syntax crayon-theme-classic-copy crayon-font-monaco crayon-os-pc print-yes notranslate" data-settings=" minimize scroll-mouseover" style="max-width: 900px; margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; font-size: 12px !important; line-height: 15px !important; height: auto;">
		
			<div class="crayon-plain-wrap"><textarea class="crayon-plain print-no" data-settings="dblclick" readonly="readonly" style="tab-size: 4; font-size: 12px !important; line-height: 15px !important; z-index: 0; opacity: 0; overflow: hidden;" wrap="soft">
&lt;?php

$instance = new class {};	
</textarea></div>
			<div class="crayon-main" style="max-width: 900px; position: relative; z-index: 1; overflow: hidden;">
				<table class="crayon-table" style="margin-left: -18px;">
					<tbody><tr class="crayon-row">
				<td class="crayon-nums " data-settings="hide">
					<div class="crayon-nums-content" style="font-size: 12px !important; line-height: 15px !important;"><div class="crayon-num" data-line="crayon-623de9e82a46b539003283-1">1</div><div class="crayon-num" data-line="crayon-623de9e82a46b539003283-2">2</div><div class="crayon-num" data-line="crayon-623de9e82a46b539003283-3">3</div><div class="crayon-num" data-line="crayon-623de9e82a46b539003283-4">4</div><div class="crayon-num" data-line="crayon-623de9e82a46b539003283-5">5</div></div>
				</td>
						<td class="crayon-code"><div class="crayon-pre" style="font-size: 12px !important; line-height: 15px !important; -moz-tab-size:4; -o-tab-size:4; -webkit-tab-size:4; tab-size:4;"><div class="crayon-line" id="crayon-623de9e82a46b539003283-1">&nbsp;</div><div class="crayon-line" id="crayon-623de9e82a46b539003283-2"><span class="crayon-h">&lt;</span><span class="crayon-sy">?</span><span class="crayon-i">php</span></div><div class="crayon-line" id="crayon-623de9e82a46b539003283-3">&nbsp;</div><div class="crayon-line" id="crayon-623de9e82a46b539003283-4"><span class="crayon-sy">$</span><span class="crayon-i">instance</span><span class="crayon-h"> </span>=<span class="crayon-h"> </span><span class="crayon-r">new</span><span class="crayon-h"> </span><span class="crayon-t">class</span><span class="crayon-h"> </span><span class="crayon-sy">{</span><span class="crayon-sy">}</span><span class="crayon-sy">;</span><span class="crayon-h">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></div><div class="crayon-line" id="crayon-623de9e82a46b539003283-5">&nbsp;</div></div></td>
					</tr>
				</tbody></table>
			</div>
		</div>
<!-- [Format Time: 0.0001 seconds] -->
<p></p>
<p>Открывающая фигурная скобка МОЖЕТ быть в той же строке, что и 
ключевое слово class, если список интерфейсов реализует ее. Если список 
implements переносится, фигурная скобка ДОЛЖНА быть помещена в строке, 
следующей непосредственно за последним интерфейсом.</p>
<p></p><!-- Crayon Syntax Highlighter v_2.7.2_beta -->
<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="PSR-12_files/classic-copy.css">
<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="PSR-12_files/monaco.css">

		<div id="crayon-623de9e82a46f253007467" class="crayon-syntax crayon-theme-classic-copy crayon-font-monaco crayon-os-pc print-yes notranslate" data-settings=" minimize scroll-mouseover" style="max-width: 900px; margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; font-size: 12px !important; line-height: 15px !important; height: auto;">
		
			<div class="crayon-plain-wrap"><textarea class="crayon-plain print-no" data-settings="dblclick" readonly="readonly" style="tab-size: 4; font-size: 12px !important; line-height: 15px !important; z-index: 0; opacity: 0; overflow: hidden;" wrap="soft">
&lt;?php

// Brace on the same line
$instance = new class extends \Foo implements \HandleableInterface {
    // Class content
};

// Brace on the next line
$instance = new class extends \Foo implements
    \ArrayAccess,
    \Countable,
    \Serializable
{
    // Class content
};	
</textarea></div>
			<div class="crayon-main" style="max-width: 900px; position: relative; z-index: 1; overflow: hidden;">
				<table class="crayon-table" style="margin-left: -25px;">
					<tbody><tr class="crayon-row">
				<td class="crayon-nums " data-settings="hide">
					<div class="crayon-nums-content" style="font-size: 12px !important; line-height: 15px !important;"><div class="crayon-num" data-line="crayon-623de9e82a46f253007467-1">1</div><div class="crayon-num" data-line="crayon-623de9e82a46f253007467-2">2</div><div class="crayon-num" data-line="crayon-623de9e82a46f253007467-3">3</div><div class="crayon-num" data-line="crayon-623de9e82a46f253007467-4">4</div><div class="crayon-num" data-line="crayon-623de9e82a46f253007467-5">5</div><div class="crayon-num" data-line="crayon-623de9e82a46f253007467-6">6</div><div class="crayon-num" data-line="crayon-623de9e82a46f253007467-7">7</div><div class="crayon-num" data-line="crayon-623de9e82a46f253007467-8">8</div><div class="crayon-num" data-line="crayon-623de9e82a46f253007467-9">9</div><div class="crayon-num" data-line="crayon-623de9e82a46f253007467-10">10</div><div class="crayon-num" data-line="crayon-623de9e82a46f253007467-11">11</div><div class="crayon-num" data-line="crayon-623de9e82a46f253007467-12">12</div><div class="crayon-num" data-line="crayon-623de9e82a46f253007467-13">13</div><div class="crayon-num" data-line="crayon-623de9e82a46f253007467-14">14</div><div class="crayon-num" data-line="crayon-623de9e82a46f253007467-15">15</div><div class="crayon-num" data-line="crayon-623de9e82a46f253007467-16">16</div><div class="crayon-num" data-line="crayon-623de9e82a46f253007467-17">17</div></div>
				</td>
						<td class="crayon-code"><div class="crayon-pre" style="font-size: 12px !important; line-height: 15px !important; -moz-tab-size:4; -o-tab-size:4; -webkit-tab-size:4; tab-size:4;"><div class="crayon-line" id="crayon-623de9e82a46f253007467-1">&nbsp;</div><div class="crayon-line" id="crayon-623de9e82a46f253007467-2"><span class="crayon-h">&lt;</span><span class="crayon-sy">?</span><span class="crayon-i">php</span></div><div class="crayon-line" id="crayon-623de9e82a46f253007467-3">&nbsp;</div><div class="crayon-line" id="crayon-623de9e82a46f253007467-4"><span class="crayon-c">// Brace on the same line</span></div><div class="crayon-line" id="crayon-623de9e82a46f253007467-5"><span class="crayon-sy">$</span><span class="crayon-i">instance</span><span class="crayon-h"> </span>=<span class="crayon-h"> </span><span class="crayon-r">new</span><span class="crayon-h"> </span><span class="crayon-t">class</span><span class="crayon-h"> </span><span class="crayon-r">extends</span><span class="crayon-h"> </span><span class="crayon-sy">\</span><span class="crayon-e">Foo</span><span class="crayon-h"> </span><span class="crayon-r">implements</span><span class="crayon-h"> </span><span class="crayon-sy">\</span><span class="crayon-e">HandleableInterface</span><span class="crayon-h"> </span><span class="crayon-sy">{</span></div><div class="crayon-line" id="crayon-623de9e82a46f253007467-6"><span class="crayon-h">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span class="crayon-c">// Class content</span></div><div class="crayon-line" id="crayon-623de9e82a46f253007467-7"><span class="crayon-sy">}</span><span class="crayon-sy">;</span></div><div class="crayon-line" id="crayon-623de9e82a46f253007467-8">&nbsp;</div><div class="crayon-line" id="crayon-623de9e82a46f253007467-9"><span class="crayon-c">// Brace on the next line</span></div><div class="crayon-line" id="crayon-623de9e82a46f253007467-10"><span class="crayon-sy">$</span><span class="crayon-i">instance</span><span class="crayon-h"> </span>=<span class="crayon-h"> </span><span class="crayon-r">new</span><span class="crayon-h"> </span><span class="crayon-t">class</span><span class="crayon-h"> </span><span class="crayon-r">extends</span><span class="crayon-h"> </span><span class="crayon-sy">\</span><span class="crayon-e">Foo </span><span class="crayon-r">implements</span></div><div class="crayon-line" id="crayon-623de9e82a46f253007467-11"><span class="crayon-h">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span class="crayon-sy">\</span><span class="crayon-i">ArrayAccess</span><span class="crayon-sy">,</span></div><div class="crayon-line" id="crayon-623de9e82a46f253007467-12"><span class="crayon-h">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span class="crayon-sy">\</span><span class="crayon-i">Countable</span><span class="crayon-sy">,</span></div><div class="crayon-line" id="crayon-623de9e82a46f253007467-13"><span class="crayon-h">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span class="crayon-sy">\</span><span class="crayon-e">Serializable</span></div><div class="crayon-line" id="crayon-623de9e82a46f253007467-14"><span class="crayon-sy">{</span></div><div class="crayon-line" id="crayon-623de9e82a46f253007467-15"><span class="crayon-h">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span class="crayon-c">// Class content</span></div><div class="crayon-line" id="crayon-623de9e82a46f253007467-16"><span class="crayon-sy">}</span><span class="crayon-sy">;</span><span class="crayon-h">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></div><div class="crayon-line" id="crayon-623de9e82a46f253007467-17">&nbsp;</div></div></td>
